# TabBar

`TxTabBar` renders app-style bottom navigation from an `items` array. It owns no router integration; callers bind `v-model`, react to `change`, and decide whether the selected value drives routing, filtering, or local view state.

## Basic Usage

Disable `fixed` when the tab bar is rendered inside a preview frame, modal, or custom shell instead of the viewport.

